		<div class="info">
			<h1>July 16, 2014 - Bill de Blasio</h1>
			<div class="meta">
				<ul>
					<li>Episode: 10129</li><li class="need-count"> (0)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<p>Rick Perry faces criticism over his fashion choices, Joe Quesada discusses Captain America's replacement, and Bill de Blasio weighs in on the challenges facing New Yorkers.</p>
			
		</div>
	</div>
   <div class="transcript">
