					<p>SUSTAINABLE CITY.</p>
					<p>DID SOME GOOD INVESTMENTS INEDUCATION.</p>
					<p>BUT IN THE END, HE DID NOTADDRESS INCOME INEQUALITY.</p>
					<p>HE DID NOT ADDRESS STOP ANDFRISK.</p>
					<p>HE DIDN'T ADDRESS A NUMBEROF ISSUES THAT WERE TEARING</p>
					<p>CITY AND DEMAND ARESOLUTION.</p>
					<p>&gt;&gt; YOU ADDRESSED STOP ANDFRISK.</p>
					<p>YOU STOPPED STOP AND FRISKAS WE KNOW IT BUT THE</p>
